    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#ghislanzoni1925"/>, pp. <citedRange>411-413</citedRange></bibl>, whence 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>9.112</citedRange></bibl>; 
                    <bibl> <ptr target="#laronde1987"/>, p. <citedRange>117</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#cdl1998a"/><citedRange/></bibl>, whence 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>48.2055</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>020000</citedRange></bibl>.
                    Cf. <bibl><ptr target="#chamoux1958"/>, p. <citedRange>580</citedRange></bibl>, whence 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>17.795</citedRange></bibl>; 
                    <bibl> <ptr target="#stucchi1975"/>, p. <citedRange>91</citedRange></bibl>; 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#marquaille2003"/>, pp. <citedRange>27-28</citedRange></bibl>, and 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#cdlBE"/>, <citedRange>2005.620</citedRange></bibl>, whence 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>53.2028</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#rosamilia2023"/>, p. <citedRange>102</citedRange> (prosopography), p. <citedRange>205-206</citedRange> (date), p. <citedRange>371</citedRange>, number 97(text)</bibl>. </p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><persName type="attested" key=""><name nymRef="#Νικόβωλος"><supplied reason="lost">Νικόβ</supplied>ωλος</name> <persName type="attested" key=""><name type="patronymic" nymRef="#Ἰάσων">Ἰάσο<supplied reason="lost">νος</supplied></name></persName></persName>
                    <lb n="2"/><w lemma="βασιλεύς"><supplied reason="lost">βασιλέ</supplied>ως</w> <persName type="ruler" key="Magas"><name nymRef="#Μάγας">Mάγα</name></persName> 
                        <rs type="office" key="priest"><w lemma="ἱαριτεύω">ἱαριτ<supplied reason="lost">εύων</supplied></w></rs>
                    <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">τοῖς</supplied> <w lemma="θεός"><supplied reason="lost">θεοῖς</supplied></w> <supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied>οῖς 
                        <w>ἐν</w> τᾶι <w lemma="ἀγορά">ἀγορᾶι</w> <w lemma="ἀνατίθημι">ἀνέθ<supplied reason="lost">ηκε</supplied></w>.
	 </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p>
                    <app loc="1">
                        <lem><supplied reason="lost" resp="#laronde1987 #cdl1998a">Νικόβ</supplied>ωλος</lem>
                        <rdg resp="#chamoux1958 #stucchi1975"><supplied reason="lost">Πολύβ</supplied>ωλος</rdg>
                        <rdg resp="#ghislanzoni1925"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">β</supplied>ωλος</rdg>
                    </app>
               </p>
 </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><supplied reason="lost">Nikob</supplied>olos fils d'Iasôn, alors qu'il était prêtre du <supplied reason="lost">roi</supplied> Magas, a consacré <supplied reason="subaudible">ce monument</supplied> <supplied reason="lost">aux dieux</supplied> de l'agora.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><supplied reason="lost">Nikob</supplied>olos son of Iason, being priest of <supplied reason="lost">king</supplied> Magas, dedicated <supplied reason="subaudible">this monument</supplied> <supplied reason="lost">to the gods</supplied> of the agora.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><supplied reason="lost">Nikob</supplied>olos figlio di Iason, quando era sacerdote del <supplied reason="lost">re</supplied> Magas, ha dedicato <supplied reason="subaudible">questo monumento</supplied> <supplied reason="lost">agli dèi</supplied> dell'agora.</p>
            </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>For king Magas and his cult, see <bibl><ptr target="#chamoux1958"/></bibl> and <bibl><ptr target="#marquaille2003"/></bibl>.</p>
                <p>The priest's name is restored with certainty by comparison with <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr065200</ref>, l. 1.</p>
                <p/>
            </div></body>
    </text>
